<collectingCountry box="[1065,1104,1789,1810]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">UK</collectingCountry>
with registration number 2010:11:7:3. Another two slides are deposited in the Laboratory of Protozoology, Ocean University of 
<collectingCountry box="[826,895,1881,1903]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">China</collectingCountry>
(no. PHB 
<date box="[1012,1126,1881,1903]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1509-09-12">09121509</date>
).
</paragraph>
